      <title>社會共構：民主是一種理想的制度嗎？</title>
      <link>https://rutopio.github.io/essay/2017-03-19-%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E5%85%B1%E6%A7%8B%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E7%A8%AE%E7%90%86%E6%83%B3%E7%9A%84%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E5%97%8E/</link>
